-- UniCredit could use 14-15 bln euros of ECB's TLTRO, around half in Italy
-- By Stephen Jewkes
-- Thu Jul 10, 2014 02:54AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, July 10 (Reuters) - Unicredit <CRDI.MI> could draw on 14-15 billion euros of the European Central Bank's fresh long-term refinancing operations known as TLTRO, the bank's CEO said in an interview on Thursday, confirmed by a spokesman for the lender.

